title: Palm Reading - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/1/22
itunes:title: Palm Reading - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/1/22
description:
George Noory and psychic Vernon Mahabal discuss how the lines on your hand can give you a road map to events in your life, how your left and right hands give you different insights, and whether he would tell people bad events he sees in their palms.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
